  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b85\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0bb0 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcb\u0bb3\u0bcd !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Urgent appeal to the public of the three forces!",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "We request the general public to cooperate with the three forces to maintain peace until a new president is elected in the country.",
        "In addition, Chief of Defense Staff General Shavendra Silva said that damage to the country's national assets, private or government assets should be avoided.",
        "Following the demonstrations in Colombo on Wednesday the 13th and the takeover of the Prime Minister's Office by the demonstrators, the Chief of Defense Staff General Savendra Silva, Inspector General of Police CD Wickramaratne, Army Commander Lt. Gen. Vikum Lianake, Air Force Commander Air Marshal Sudarshana Pathirana and Navy Commander Vice Admiral Nishantha Ulukethenna jointly issued a special announcement.",
        "General Shavendra Silva, who said the above, further mentioned,",
        "The country's armed forces and police are working under the existing constitution. The Speaker informed us that President Gotabaya Rajapaksa will resign on the 13th.",
        "With the resignation of the President, we also discussed with him the steps to be taken in the period until a new President is appointed in the coming days.",
        "We have requested the Speaker to conduct a discussion with all the party leaders and clarify the system of running the administration of the country till a political president is appointed. We have also requested you to inform us about the political decision to be taken in this regard.",
        "We hope that the speaker and party leaders will inform the people of this. Therefore, we request the general public, including the youth, to maintain peace until this announcement is made and the next president is elected.",
        "We also request cooperation from the three forces to maintain peace. Accordingly, we request the three forces to cooperate without causing any damage to the country's national assets, private or government assets, he said."
      ],
